Four days until Jency and Aaron’s first feature film premieres @manshiptheatre 

Get your tickets for the 2:00pm showing here:

https://www.manshiptheatre.org/show/days-of-daisy-louisiana-premier

On the eve of my 40th birthday, I was honored with my favorite human on the planet @jencyghogan to be on the cover of the @brbizreport Dec 2022 issue for an article about local filmmakers and the film industry here. This is significant  because I was depressed last month I didn’t make it in time to be nominated earlier in the year for their #fortyunderforty event. I was out of state the entire summer in Maine taking cinematography classes. But this was an honor to see this today unexpectedly. Thanks @collinrichiephoto for the awesome photo in our studio. Can’t wait to make our next film. This came just two days after the Baton Rouge premier of our film screening @daysofdaisyfilm at the @manshiptheatre. Thanks for all your support!

Looking for beauty industry tenant in our wonderful suite looking to own their own business. Hair, eyebrows, skin care, etc! Who do you know who would want this? Share with them and have them call me.
To the dopest crew in the photo biz- I love doing life with you guys. Thanks to this bunch of photographers for being friends first, and for celebrating my 40th birthday in style. Love you guys.

Eye Wander’s humble beginnings. My first office for Eye Wander Photo was in my bedroom at my parent’s home for 8 years (2002-2010). My first employee besides my mother edited in my bedroom next to me. My grandmother took these photos - she was a true documentarian. She took photos and video of everything. Insignificant details that later become so important.
